=== "VRave"（ヴレイヴ） ===
On July 30, 2023, the music live event “VRave” was held at Akihabara Entas. This live event featured artists active in VR and also served as a prelude to the music-focused VR event “MusicVket 5,” scheduled for August.

Starting with DJ [https://twitter.com/kgtr0610_vrchat Kagetora], the lineup featured diverse genres. idol unit “[https://twitter.com/Suc_Suquel Suc×Suquel.]”, rock band “[https://twitter.com/LAUTRIV_ LAUTRIV]”, hip-hop unit “[https://twitter.com/CROWK_OFFICIAL CROWK]”, music unit “[https://twitter.com/VrcYss YSS]”, vocal duo ‘[https://x.com/AMOKA_info AMOKA]’, and blues rock band “JOHNNY HENRY”... Joined by VTuber [https://twitter.com/tmgnrei ChumuNote], a total of eight acts took the stage at Entas.

== Volunteer-led activities ==

===== VketReal in Sapporo =====
VketReal is a completely volunteer-run event organized by passionate users of VketReal, with [https://vrchat.com/home/user/usr_9ecddc22-5f86-4da2-8ee4-0e2197215487 A-kun] serving as its representative.

On Monday, July 21, 2025 (a national holiday), “[https://vris.jp/en/2025Summer VketReal in Sapporo]”  was held by a group of enthusiastic users. In addition to the Sapporo TV Tower venue, diverse events including talks, live performances, and DJ sessions were held, attracting over 1,000 participants in total. This success has further accelerated the movement to expand VketReal nationwide through user-led initiatives.

==== VketReal Unofficial Garage Developers（VRUGD） ====
[https://www.vrugd.jp VketReal Unofficial Garage Developers (VRUGD)] is a volunteer development team community formed by staff members within the VketReal volunteer staff team who voluntarily gather to develop the system.This community develops useful tools for enjoying the stamp rally app used at  “[https://vris.jp/en/2025Summer VketReal in Sapporo]” and the main VketReal event hosted by HIKKY Co., Ltd..

It continues to collaborate with various parties on development and is one of the noteworthy communities run by volunteers.

